<p>If you are lonely, then why are you spending so much time alone writing a blog? Especially when you have to spend so much time alone writing stuff for University studies, anyway.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by person at February 14, 2005 11:59 PM <a href="001560#c3964">#</a></p>

</div><div id="c3970">

<p>What do you suggest I do instead? I need something more specific than <a href="001559#c3963">&#8220;start living&#8230;take control&#8221;</a>.</p>

<p>Anyway, nowadays I write most of my entries on the back of scrap paper while I wait for class to start. I suppose I could use the time to chat up people sitting near me, but I&#8217;m really far too shy to do that even when I&#8217;m not writing blog posts.</p>

